    <published>2019-04-23T16:25:40.000Z</published>
    <updated>2019-10-31T03:40:33.627Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<!-- build time:Sat May 02 2020 11:24:37 GMT+0800 (GMT+08:00) --><p>&emsp;&emsp;最近因为毕业论文和托福考试的压力，搞得有点心烦气躁，所以决定接触新事物散散心。同时为了之后博士期间有能力兼职做网页开发赚点外快，我现在就开始学习各大主流前端框架，从<strong>Vue.js</strong>开始。本文会逐步整理本人<strong>从入门到进阶学习</strong>所遇到的坑，以及相应的填坑方法。</p><h3 id="Vue-js安装，最后“cnpm-run-dev”报错"><a href="#Vue-js安装，最后“cnpm-run-dev”报错" class="headerlink" title="Vue.js安装，最后“cnpm run dev”报错"></a>Vue.js安装，最后“cnpm run dev”报错</h3><p>我是根据<a href="http://www.runoob.com/vue2/vue-install.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">菜鸟教程</a>来进行Vue.js的安装，前面都很顺利，最后一步“cnpm run dev”报错，报错信息如下：<br><pre><code class="hljs javascript">$ cnpm run dev  &gt; my-project@<span class="hljs-number">1.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span> dev D:\vue\my-project &gt; webpack-dev-server --inline --progress --config build/webpack.dev.conf.jsnpm ERR! code ELIFECYCLEnpm ERR! errno <span class="hljs-number">1</span>npm ERR! my-project@<span class="hljs-number">1.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span> dev: <span class="hljs-string">`webpack-dev-server --inline --progress --config build/webpack.dev.conf.js`</span>npm ERR! Exit status <span class="hljs-number">1</span>npm ERR!npm ERR! Failed at the my-project@<span class="hljs-number">1.0</span><span class="hljs-number">.0</span> dev script.npm ERR! This is probably not a problem <span class="hljs-keyword">with</span> npm. There is likely additional logging output above.npm ERR! A complete log <span class="hljs-keyword">of</span> <span class="hljs-keyword">this</span> run can be found <span class="hljs-keyword">in</span>:npm ERR!     C:\Users\LapChun\AppData\Roaming\npm-cache\_logs\<span class="hljs-number">2019</span><span class="hljs-number">-04</span><span class="hljs-number">-24</span>T12_54_21_588Z-debug.log</code></pre></p><p><strong>解决方法：这是新版webpack存在的bug,先卸载现有的新版本webpack，再安装老版本就可以了。</strong><br><pre><code class="hljs undefined">cnpm uninstall webpack-dev-servercnpm install webpack-dev-server@2.9.1cnpm run dev</code></pre></p><p>依次执行上述3条命令，问题得以解决。</p><h2 id="参考资料"><a href="#参考资料" class="headerlink" title="参考资料"></a>参考资料</h2><blockquote><ul><li><a href="http://www.runoob.com/vue2/vue-install.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vue.js 安装</a></li><li><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/charming18/article/details/87991072" target="_blank" rel="noopener">vue 项目，下载别人的项目和npm run dev报错解决方法</a></li></ul></blockquote><!-- rebuild by neat -->]]></content>
    
